    <h4>Guest Information</h4>
    <h5>Accomedations</h5>
    <p> For the adventuresome guest, camping will be allowed at the Rigmore house!
    You are encouraged to bring your tent and sleeping bag and sleep out underneith the
    stars.  Those guest who live near by and do not feel comfortable driving home are also
    encouraged to camp. There is a huge grassy field and a fire pit, so there will be
    plenty of space to accomedate everyone wishing to camp. Bathrooms and showers are also
    availiable inside the Rigmore house.  </p>

    <p> For those who would rather sleep in a bed (lame!), the official wedding hotel is the <a
    href="http://hamptoninn3.hilton.com/en/hotels/north-carolina/hampton-inn-and-suites-chapel-hill-durham-area-RDUCHHX/index.html">Hampton
    Inn and Suites</a>: <br>
    6121 Farrington Road <br>
    North Carolina 27517 <br>
    This hotel is located 25 minutes from the Rigmore house and 15 minutes from the RDU
    airport.  Rooms can be reserved for
    $109/night using the code ???. A shuttle service will be availiable for those wishing
    to return to the hotel after the reception.  </p>
    
    <p> An alternate hotel is the <a
    href="http://www.ihg.com/holidayinnexpress/hotels/us/en/chapel-hill/rdufr/hoteldetail">Holliday
    Inn Express</a>, convieniently located next to the Hampton Inn: <br>
    6119 Farrington Road <br>
    North Carolina 27517 </p>

